---
import CathedralLayout from '../layouts/CathedralLayout.astro';
---

<CathedralLayout title="AI Policy - ホーム">
<div class="home">
<header class="home-header">
<div class="seal">
<svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="var(--divine-gold)">
<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" stroke-width="2" />
<rect x="35" y="35" width="30" height="30" stroke-width="1" transform="rotate(45 50 50)" />
</svg>
</div>
<p class="preamble">社内向けAIポリシー</p>
<h1>AI Policy</h1>
<p class="subtitle">エンジニアリング・開発業務における AI 活用の指針</p>
</header>

<nav class="page-list">
<a href="/AI-policy/policy" class="page-card">
<div class="card-icon">
<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
<path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
<polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
<line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/>
<line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/>
<polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="card-body">
<h2>AI活用原則と遵守事項</h2>
<p>エンジニアリング・開発業務における AI 活用の基本原則、絶対遵守事項、利用ガイドラインを定めた中心的なポリシー文書。</p>
</div>
<span class="card-arrow">→</span>
</a>

<a href="/AI-policy/input-guidelines" class="page-card">
<div class="card-icon">
<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
<line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/>
<line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="card-body">
<h2>入力してはいけない情報リスト</h2>
<p>生成AIに入力禁止の情報（個人情報・機密情報・認証情報など）と、安全に入力できる情報の基準をまとめた実務向け指針。</p>
</div>
<span class="card-arrow">→</span>
</a>

<a href="/AI-policy/training-achievements" class="page-card">
<div class="card-icon">
<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
<path d="M3 18h18"/>
<path d="M7 18V8"/>
<path d="M12 18V5"/>
<path d="M17 18v-6"/>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="card-body">
<h2>3ヶ月研修成果物一覧</h2>
<p>PoC・Webアプリ・CI/CD自動化・ガバナンス資料まで、研修期間中に作成した成果物をカテゴリ別にまとめた一覧ページ。</p>
</div>
<span class="card-arrow">→</span>
</a>
</nav>
</div>
</CathedralLayout>

<style>
.home {
min-height: 100vh;
max-width: 850px;
margin: 0 auto;
padding: 6rem 2.5rem;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: center;
}

.home-header {
text-align: center;
margin-bottom: 5rem;
padding: 2.4rem 2rem;
background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
box-shadow: 0 16px 42px rgba(9, 25, 46, 0.12);
backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
border-radius: 20px;
width: 100%;
}

.seal {
margin-bottom: 2rem;
opacity: 0.8;
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
}

.preamble {
text-transform: uppercase;
font-size: 0.85rem;
letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
color: var(--stone-text);
margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

h1 {
font-family: var(--font-serif);
font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
font-weight: 400;
line-height: 1.15;
margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
color: var(--obsidian-text);
}

.subtitle {
font-size: 1rem;
color: var(--stone-text);
line-height: 1.8;
}

.page-list {
width: 100%;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
gap: 1.5rem;
}

.page-card {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 1.5rem;
padding: 2rem;
border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84);
text-decoration: none;
color: inherit;
transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
backdrop-filter: blur(9px);
border-radius: 18px;
box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(9, 25, 46, 0.1);
}

.page-card:hover {
border-color: var(--divine-gold);
box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
}

.card-icon {
flex-shrink: 0;
color: var(--divine-gold);
opacity: 0.9;
}

.card-body {
flex: 1;
}

.card-body h2 {
font-family: var(--font-serif);
font-size: 1.3rem;
font-weight: 400;
margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
color: var(--obsidian-text);
}

.card-body p {
font-size: 0.95rem;
color: var(--stone-text);
line-height: 1.7;
margin: 0;
}

.card-arrow {
font-size: 1.2rem;
color: var(--divine-gold);
flex-shrink: 0;
transition: transform 0.2s;
}

.page-card:hover .card-arrow {
transform: translateX(4px);
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
.home {
padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
}
.home-header {
padding: 1.9rem 1.3rem;
}
.page-card {
flex-wrap: wrap;
}
}
</style>
